Syntax: spinfist

Executes a spinning fist technique that strikes all enemies in the room
simultaneously. Unlike most targeted attacks, spinfist hits every opponent
present (excluding grouped allies and your master). This makes it highly
effective against multiple enemies.

Effects:
  - Attempts one_hit() against each eligible target in the room.
  - Costs chi (scales with cooldown if recently used).
  - Activates a 10-round cooldown preventing reuse.

Each target is checked individually -- enemies that are immune or protected
may not be affected. Grouped or following characters are not hit.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Must have chi available.
  - Must have the Spinfist skill learned.

See also: shelp spinfist flurry aurabolt phantomfist
